10:27.833 --> 10:29.250
And that was sad.

10:31.291 --> 10:34.416
(street noise)

10:37.125 --> 10:39.750
Cris:
<i>I moved to California,</i>

10:39.833 --> 10:42.625
<i>and I was in</i>
<i>a woman's bookstore</i>

10:42.708 --> 10:43.708
<i>in the Mission</i>

10:43.791 --> 10:46.333
