You know?

13:03.875 --> 13:05.625
It was great.
They loved the idea.

13:05.708 --> 13:07.375
It was like a feather in
their cap or whatever.

13:07.458 --> 13:10.666
Russo:
<i>And I think they also</i>
<i>liked the idea of...</i>

13:10.750 --> 13:13.833
-you know, helping
create gay families.
-Gay families. Yeah.

13:13.916 --> 13:15.375
It was like this
whole new thing,

13:15.458 --> 13:17.125
and they were on
the cutting edge.

13:17.208 --> 13:19.291
♪ ♪

13:19.375 --> 13:23.625
Cris:
