13:33.041 --> 13:34.791
Robin:
<i>Cris had told us that</i>

13:34.875 --> 13:37.500
he spoke five languages
or seven languages.

13:37.583 --> 13:39.666
That he was very smart.

13:39.750 --> 13:42.791
Russo:
<i>And we liked the idea of the</i>
<i>donor being in San Francisco,</i>

13:42.875 --> 13:44.708
<i>which was gonna be far away.</i>

13:44.791 --> 13:46.875
